title: Recap: Tech takes series from Iowa State - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Recap: Tech takes series from Iowa State - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: AMES, Iowa – A nine-run second inning was all Texas Tech (21-20, 4-8) needed to take down Iowa State (21-21, 2-7) in five innings, 9-1, to claim the Big 12 series win.
